{"tid":561420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"董建華前助理路祥安病逝　疑流感奪命","createTime":"2018-02-15T03:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T04:45:40.000Z","uid":53003,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7a9cfabfc4bf10aa94c479594beec9cffa043e46","tid":561420,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:58:04.000Z","msg":"政圈傳出在前特首董建華年代出任特首辦高級特別助理、現任香港中華能源基金會副秘書長路祥安病逝，《明報》記者透過第三者找中華能源基金會前同事，對方證實該消息。<br />\n<br />\n《星島日報》報道，路祥安本周一疑因感染流感入住瑪麗 院，短短兩天病情急劇轉差病逝。報道引述醫生估計，路祥安可能因流感引發腦炎或心肌炎，嚴重者可導致心衰竭、呼吸困難等，更可能於短期內死亡。<br />\n<br />\n現年66歲的路祥安，原是東方海外高層，1997年後隨董建華加入政府任特首辦高級特別助理。他於2000年捲入「港大民調風波」，被指向時任港大民意研究計劃主任鍾庭耀施壓，要求停止進行特首及政府民調，港大之後成立獨立調查小組調查。他至2001年底辭職，2010年起出任中華能源基金委員副秘書長。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180215/s00001/1518666627414?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180215%2Fs00001%2F1518666627414%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=X8FF1IDY7L640IgtqOALI26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=2b1028cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180215%2Fs00001%2F1518666627414%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=a068f696\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180215/s00001/1518666627414?web_push=1</a>"},{"pid":"b2511b4d8546c649cafaac635056ef386cf3e82b","tid":561420,"uid":7534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T04:03:15.000Z","msg":"今晚開香檳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5c56540e142d44164714254e8e3fb190672416","tid":561420,"uid":56321,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T04:03:25.000Z","msg":"惡有惡報，若然未報&hellip;&hellip;<br />\nBTW<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />